            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Get my free audit <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">24-hour delivery · No card</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="vs-stacc">theStacc vs Anyword — different jobs, honest comparison</h2>
        <p>Anyword and theStacc do not directly compete — we serve different jobs. But here is the comparison most marketers actually want to see.</p>

        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Anyword</th><th>theStacc</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Starting price</td><td>$39/mo</td><td>$99/mo</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Predictive Performance Score</td><td class="cell-yes">Unique to Anyword</td><td class="cell-no">Not the goal</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Built for paid ads (Meta / Google)</td><td class="cell-yes">Primary use case</td><td class="cell-no">Not included</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Built for SEO blog posts</td><td>Possible, not optimized</td><td class="cell-yes">Primary use case</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Articles auto-published to CMS</td><td class="cell-no">Manual export</td><td class="cell-yes">WordPress · Webflow · Ghost</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Google Business Profile posts</td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-yes">30 GBP posts / month</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Rank tracking</td><td class="cell-no">No</td><td class="cell-yes">Daily</td></tr>
