        <h2 id="performance">Performance — does the Predictive Score actually predict?</h2>
        <p>We ran 12 A/B tests on Meta Ads (e-commerce niche, $2K total spend, 600+ impressions per ad). For each test, we paired Anyword copy scoring 80+ against Anyword copy scoring &lt;60. Results:</p>

        <div class="stat-grid">
