          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">9 / 12</div><div class="stat-lbl">Tests where high-score won</div></div>
          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">$0.41</div><div class="stat-lbl">CPC on high-score copy (vs $0.58)</div></div>
          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">~30%</div><div class="stat-lbl">Time saved vs writing copy manually</div></div>
